<p>*In North Carolina, if you miss the registration deadline, you may be eligible to register&nbsp;and vote or make changes to your voter registration (anything other than party affiliation) and vote during the early voting period<b>.</b>&nbsp;Learn more at&nbsp;<a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="d65bb5f0-ef3c-4ea3-a66f-d0407be1c8bc" href="https://www.ncsbe.gov/registering/how-register/register-person-during-early-voting" title="Register in Person During Early Voting">Register in Person During Early Voting.</a></p>

